Indoor/Outdoor Usage
Outdoor
  • Flawless 2K Clarity with 145° FOV: N1 wireless cameras for home security captures more of your surroundings with ultra-wide 145° lens and delivers crisp 2K HD videos with vivid details both day and night. With Color Night Vision and 8X Digital Zoom, you'll never miss a thing even far from 6m and receive instant alerts of anything suspicious.
  • No Monthly Fees and 16TB Expandable Local Storage: Feel secure knowing there are no subscription fees. Our H1 HomeStation boasts 16GB of eMMC storage, expandable to 16TB(*Note: Hard Drive Not Included), which can cover your lifetime storage needs. Rest assured, your privacy is guaranteed with TÜV Rheinland certifications. Plus, AES+RSA encryption safeguards your data, ensuring it's accessible only to you.
  • 210-Day Battery Life with IP67: Our powerful 7,800mAh battery provides an extraordinary 210 days of crystal-clear surveillance on a single charge. Even in extreme temperatures ranging from -4°F to 122°F, our IP67-rated outdoor security camera offers long-term peace of mind with minimal maintenance. *NOTE: 210-Day Battery life is based on lab data with 10 seconds of video per recording, 30 recordings per day. Our wireless security cameras are best suited for outdoor use because battery life varies with the frequency of events and recording length.
  • Instant Alert & Flexible Installation: Stay updated with human tracking, offering quick notifications and snapshots when anyone approaches, lingers, or passes by your home, quickly responding to security issues. With its wire-free design, you can easily set our wireless security camera up anywhere in minutes.*NOTE: To ensure full functionality of your security camera, please download the "baseus Security" app.
  • 2-Year Warranty & Lifetime Tech Support: Find comfort in our 2-year warranty, securing your investment. Our lifelong technical support ensures any queries are promptly resolved, offering continuous assistance throughout your product's lifetime. *What‘s More, Our HomeStation supports up to 8 cameras to connect. With N1 add on cameras, you can build a better home security system.
  • *Note: The N1 2-Cam Kit does not support 24/7 continuous recording. It is battery powered and strikes a good balance between battery life and event capture. It records only when the camera captures moving objects.

      • What is the max range from HomeStation to the camera?

        Typically the distance from the HomeStation to the camera can be up to 20-30 feet. Actual range can be affected by a variety of factors sucth as wall thickness, obstructions in the house, and the location of the HomeStation.

      • Can the HomeStation be connected via Wi-Fi as well?

        No, HomeStation can only connect via Ethernet and it's not supported to connect with WiFi.

      • What can I do if HomeStation goes offline?

        Please check whether the LED indicator light of the HomeStation is blue. If it is red, which indicates that the network connection is abnormal, please check if the network cable is loose, or restart the router.

      • Does the Baseus Camera system support 7x24 recording?

        No, it's not supported to record 7/24. The N1 camera is battery powered. The N1 strikes a good balance between battery life and event capture only when the camera captures moving objects.

      • How to reduce invalid alerts and avoid overconsumption of power?

        Please try the following adjustments:

        1. Reduce motion detection sensitivity.

        2. Set activity areas to filter out motion detection in inactive areas.

        3. Adjust the camera's perspective to avoid sidewalks and road.

Pas besoin d'abonnement pour garder ses vidéos, le tout est stocké en local avec possibilité d'étendre le stockage via disque sata complémentaire (jusqu'à 16To accepté) (Arlo c'est minimum 5€/mois dans le cloud pour 30 jours, faites le compte). L'appairage des caméras, de la station de stockage et mises à jour des firmwares se font aisément. Dans l'application on peut gérer les zones d'enregistrement ou zones privées. Le seul bémol c'est qu'on doit travailler avec au maximum 2 rectangles pour délimiter les zones alors qu'Arlo permet par exemple de faire une forme adaptée à al surface que l'on veut surveiller. La station permet d'accueillir jusqu'à 8 caméras donc on peut supposer que les caméras seront disponibles à la pièce par la suite. La durée de vie des caméras est données pour 210 jours. Elles sont installées depuis 3 semaines et celle qui déclenche entre 8 et 10 fois par jours est encore à 90% (10% en 20 jours, ça devrait tenir ses promesses mais à voir sur le long terme). L'autre est toujours à 99% de batterie. Bref excellent petit kit pour celui qui ne veut pas mettre une fortune et extrêmement simple à mettre en œuvre. Je recommande !!
